highlights.text: “Better” by Khalid is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #21.
“Closer” by The Chainsmokers and Halsey has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 91 weeks straight.
Eminem has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lucky You (feat. Joyner Lucas)” is the highest at #2.
“Love Someone” by Lukas Graham is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 73 spots at #96.
